It's nice...



It's a nice bed. The best part, and the reason I went Casper, was price and the elimination of noisy springs. Took me about a week and a half to get used to it's firmer feel but I'm used to it now and sleep fine. It's a good mattress but I don't think it's the life changing mattress that some of the reviews claim it is. 





