Slightly better than the floor 



My lower back is in so much pain when I wake up. Even when I try to fall asleep my back hurts so badly I want to cry because I know I will be having yet another night of terrible sleep. I look forward to sleeping on hotel mattresses because they are more comfortable. This mattress is great for a lot of people but for me it just does not work. I even have the mattress topper they provided me and it does not work 





